<div class="content" name="ScmRequestInfoData" uuid="14a35c90-ff41-4608-9c20-7e99531ee3e2"><p>The ScmRequestInfoData structure contains a <a href="c13cfd00-2ab2-4d4a-8b6b-fa565671e748" data-linktype="relative-path">customREMOTE_REQUEST_SCM_INFO</a>
structure.</p><p>CLSID_ScmRequestInfo (see section <a href="c25391af-f59e-40da-885e-cc84076673e4" data-linktype="relative-path">1.9</a>) is used to identify
this property in the CustomHeader.pclsid array.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct tagScmRequestInfoData {
   DWORD* pdwReserved;
   customREMOTE_REQUEST_SCM_INFO* remoteRequest;
 } ScmRequestInfoData;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>pdwReserved:</b>   This MUST be set to
NULL and MUST be ignored on receipt.</p><p><b>remoteRequest:</b>   This MUST specify a
customREMOTE_REQUEST_SCM_INFO structure. This field MUST NOT be NULL. </p></div>